data.description: Move-in-ready and close to all conveniences in Grand Blanc. Open main level floor plan  great for entertaining or everyday living. Large kitchen opens to Living Room with cozy fire place. Fenced in back yard with patio and mature trees.  Lower Level has family room and laundry room with walk out access to back yard. 2 car attached garage.
